'''乔瓦尼·玛丽亚·维安'''（{{lang-it|Giovanni Maria Vian}}；{{bd|1952年|3月10日||}}）是一位[[意大利|意大利]]教父[[语文学|语文学]]教授和[[记者|记者]]。维安出生于[[罗马|罗马]]。他於2007年至2018年間担任《[[罗马观察报|罗马观察报]]》主编，2018年榮休，現為該報的的「榮休主任」。

==编者事业==
作为罗马观察报的主编，他不得不面对过报纸是否对[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]政府做出无根据支持的争议。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholicnewsagency.com/new.php?n=16067 |title=Editor of Vatican newspaper says ‘Obama is not pro-abortion’ |accessdate=2016-07-23 |archive-date=2009-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090625164937/http://www.catholicnewsagency.com/new.php?n=16067 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在他担任主编期间，报纸也因为称赞《[[哈利·波特|哈利·波特]]》和[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]而引人关注。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lifesitenews.com/ldn/2009/jul/09071404.html |title=Vatican Paper Heaps Praise on Harry Potter film |accessdate=2016-07-23 |archive-date=2009-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090717064504/http://www.lifesitenews.com/ldn/2009/jul/09071404.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他於2007年開始出任《[[羅馬觀察報|羅馬觀察報]]》總編輯，11年後榮休。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Glatz |first1=Carol |title=Pope names Italian journalists to key posts in Vatican communications |url=https://www.ncronline.org/news/media/pope-names-italian-journalists-key-posts-vatican-communications |accessdate=2019-07-20 |agency=Catholic News Service |publisher=National Catholic Reporter |date=2018-12-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720171117/https://www.ncronline.org/news/media/pope-names-italian-journalists-key-posts-vatican-communications |archivedate=2019-07-20 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>榮休後轉為該報的「榮休主任」。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 18.12.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/18/181218c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720165341/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/18/181218c.html |archivedate=2019-07-20 |language=en |date=2018-12-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

